  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized controlled trial (RCT) in patients who underwent sphincter preserving surgery
      due to rectal cancer. The study will analyze the effect of Transanal irrigation (TAI) and
      medication that can help control of the bowel movement in patients with low anterior
      resection syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
