  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients that have undergone surgery for rectal cancer (sphincter saving surgery, low
             anterior resection)

          -  Adult ≥ 18 years old

          -  Have scoring major LARS (according to the Low anterior resection syndrome score)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  stoma

          -  recurrent disease

          -  Another colorectal surgery

          -  Inflammatory bowel disease (IBD)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
